body:
I created an [example script on gist](https://gist.github.com/DavidWiesner/c6af3238a90b3a8b1209543a9f8d7127#file-flowers-nasnet-sh) with tensorflow models and the large nasnet. This script were run on the official tensorflow docker images.
On my Tesla V100 for tensorflow 1.8-devel-gpu-py3 I got around
